            "creation_date": 1529157026,
            "body": "<p>To help you getting started, you can find documentation on how to add a floating button <a href=\"https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/ui/floating-action-button\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">here<\/a>. To make it start a new activity after cliking, add the instruction in the listener:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>FloatingActionButton fab = findViewById(R.id.fab);\nfab.setOnClickListener(new View.OnClickListener() \n{\n   @Override\n   public void onClick(View view) \n   {\n       startActivity(new Intent(this, YourNewActivity.class));\n    }\n}); \n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
